60|$|However, the sun {{which has}} such {{strength}} to kill noxious things, puts {{an end to}} ghosts more quickly even {{than it does to}} other evil vapours and emanations, and when I woke up to find it shining brilliantly in a pure heaven, <b>I</b> <b>laughed</b> <b>with</b> much heartiness over the whole affair.|$|R
