6000|$|Still, I'd go {{the world}} with Beauty, [...] <b>I</b> would <b>laugh</b> <b>with</b> her and sing, I would shun divinest duty [...] To resume her worshipping. But she'd scorn my brave endeavour, [...] She would not balm the breeze By murmuring [...] "Thine for ever!" [...] As she did upon this leaze.|$|R
